#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:818 ../../remote_sensing.rst:913
#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1229 ../../remote_sensing.rst:1250
#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1272
msgid ":math:`n` = number of image bands."
msgstr ":math:`n` = número de bandas de la imagen."

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:820
msgid ""
"Therefore, the distance is calculated for every pixel in the image, "
"assigning the class of the spectral signature that is closer, according to "
"the following discriminant function (adapted from Richards and Jia, 2006):"
msgstr ""
"Por lo tanto, la distancia es calculada para cada pixel en la imagen, "
"asignando la clase de la firma espectral más cercana de acuerdo a la "
"siguiente función discriminante (adaptado de Richards and Jia, 2006):"

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:824
msgid ""
"x \\in C_k \\iff d(x, y_k) < d(x, y_j) \\forall k \\neq j\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:829 ../../remote_sensing.rst:863
#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:922
msgid ":math:`C_k` = land cover class :math:`k`;"
msgstr ":math:`C_k` = clase de cobertura :math:`k`;"

