":math:`A_{L}` = Band-specific additive rescaling factor from Landsat "
"metadata (RADIANCE_ADD_BAND_x, where x is the band number)"
msgstr ""
":math:`A_{L}` = Factor aditivo de reescalamiento específico de la banda, "
"proveniente de los metadatos (RADIANCE_MULT_BAND_x, donde x es el número de "
"banda)"

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1674
