#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1682
msgid "Top Of Atmosphere (TOA) Reflectance"
msgstr "Reflectancia en el Techo de la Atmósfera (TOA)"

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1684
msgid ""
"Images in radiance can be converted to Top Of Atmosphere (TOA) Reflectance "
"(combined surface and atmospheric reflectance) in order to reduce the in "
"between-scene variability through a normalization for solar irradiance. This"
" TOA reflectance (:math:`\\rho_{p}`), which is the unitless ratio of "
"reflected versus total power energy (NASA, 2011), is calculated by:"
msgstr ""
"Es posible convertir imágenes con valores de radiancia a valores de "
"Reflectancia en el Techo de la Atmósfera (TOA), la cual combina la "
"reflectancia de la superficie y la reflectancia atmosférica, para reducir la"
" variabilidad inter-imagen a través de una normalización de la irradiancia "
"solar. Esta reflectancia TOA (:math:`\\rho_{p}`), la cual es el ratio de la "
"energía reflejada con respecto al total de la energía incidente (NASA, "
"2011), puede ser calculada como:"

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1690
msgid ""
"\\rho_{p} = (\\pi * L_{\\lambda} * d^{2} )/ (ESUN_{\\lambda} * cos\\theta_{s})\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1695
msgid ""
":math:`L_{\\lambda}` = Spectral radiance at the sensor's aperture (at-"
"satellite radiance)"
msgstr ""
":math:`L_{\\lambda}` = Radiancia espectral en el sensor (Radiancia en el "
"satélite)"

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1697
msgid ""
":math:`d` = Earth-Sun distance in astronomical units (provided with Landsat "
"8 metadata file, and an excel file is available from "
"http://landsathandbook.gsfc.nasa.gov/excel_docs/d.xls )"
msgstr ""

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1700
msgid ":math:`ESUN_{\\lambda}` = Mean solar exo-atmospheric irradiances"
msgstr ":math:`ESUN_{\\lambda}` = Irradiancia Media Solar exo-atmosférica"

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1701
msgid ""
":math:`\\theta_{s}` = Solar zenith angle in degrees, which is equal to "
":math:`\\theta_{s}` = 90° - :math:`\\theta_{e}` where :math:`\\theta_{e}` is"
" the Sun elevation"
msgstr ""
":math:`\\theta_{s}` = Angulo zenital solar en grados, el cual es equivalente"
" a: :math:`\\theta_{s}` = 90° - :math:`\\theta_{e}` donde "
":math:`\\theta_{e}` es la elevación solar"

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1705
msgid ""
"It is worth pointing out that Landsat 8 images are provided with band-"
"specific rescaling factors that allow for the direct conversion from DN to "
"TOA reflectance."
msgstr ""
"Es importante notar que para las imágenes de Landsat 8 se proveen factores "
"de reescalamiento para cada banda que permiten la conversión directa de "
"valores digitales DN a Reflectancia TOA. "

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1709
msgid ""
"Sentinel-2 images are already provided in scaled TOA reflectance, which can "
"be converted to TOA reflectance with a simple calculation using the "
"Quantification Value provided in the metadata (see "
"https://sentinel.esa.int/documents/247904/349490/S2_MSI_Product_Specification.pdf"
" )."
msgstr ""

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:1715
msgid ""
